Circo, designed in a circus theme reminiscent of the Big Top, serves upscale Italian cuisine that has received praise from The New York Times and New York Magazine. Dress is upscale casual.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please book online at the Circo website: &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.circonyc.com/reservations.html&quot;&gt;http://www.circonyc.com/reservations.html&lt;/a&gt; or contact Circo by phone at +1 212 265 3636 or email at email &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:reservations@circonyc.com&quot;&gt;reservations@circonyc.com&lt;/a&gt;to book your reservation&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mention Diners Club International Privileges Dining Collection to receive your special benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide your name, date you would like to dine, number of guests, preferred time, cell or local (hotel) phone number&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;For groups of 5 or more, Restaurant Circo requires a credit card to hold your reservation. Your credit card will not be charged at the time of booking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Please contact the restaurant by phone or email 48 hours prior to your dining date to reconfirm. Provide a reminder that this is a Diners Club International Privileges Dining Collection reservation. If you don&rsquo;t reconfirm your reservation as directed, a fee of $50 per person will charged to your credit card&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TERMS &amp;amp; CONDITIONS&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow booking instructions to ensure receiving your Privileges Dining Collection amenity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Based on Availability at the time of booking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A main course must be purchased to receive your dining benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your Privileges Dining Collection benefit may not be combined with other offers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fulfillment of the offer is the sole responsibility of the participating&nbsp;Diners Club International&nbsp;Restaurant Merchant&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Restaurant participation and benefits are subject to change or cancellation without notice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

